Shared Files:
Ekjon user arekjon user er ekta file use korte chaile shetar implementatoin ta 
kemon hobe?
 - tokhon directory structure ta ar tree nai, DAG hoye jay.
if directory contains file addresses, then problem hobe.

Solution:
1. file address NOT in directory
    put addresses in a data-structure
2. new file type : LINK type (OS eta dekhe bujhbe eta shortcut type(windows e) er ekta 
file, link type er file er data hocche path to original file.) 

